comments: Jokic (DEN) is established in a screening position as he firms up when he brushes Jones' (SAS) body during the pick.
Jones (SAS) places a resting hand on Jackson's (DEN) body as the contact that occurs after the release of the driving shot attempt is marginal.
Branham (SAS) avoids stepping out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.
Champagnie (SAS) reaches in and grazes Jokic's (DEN) arm after securing the rebound and the contact does not affect Jokic's control of the ball.
Mamukelashvili (SAS) briefly places his forearm to Jokic's (DEN) front at the start of the drive before releasing as Jokic is able to move through the contact in the backcourt.
Wembanyama (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position as he moves alongside Jokic's (DEN) path during the drive in the post.
Wembanyama (SAS) establishes himself in Jackson's (DEN) path and is firming up when he absorbs the incoming contact during the screen.
Gordon (DEN) places a resting hand on Wembanyama's (SAS) body as he moves alongside Wembanyama's path during the drive before releasing, which is marginal.
Gordon (DEN) moves alongside Wembanyama's (SAS) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he contests the driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) releases from Wembanyama (SAS) as both players come together during the drive as the contact does not affect Wembanyama's ability to defend.
Champagnie (SAS) briefly places his hand to Jackson's (DEN) front at the start of the drive, which he is able to move through.
Wembanyama (SAS) cleanly blocks Jackson's (DEN) driving shot attempt.
Gordon (DEN) cleanly deflects the incoming pass away from Mamukelashvili (SAS).
The ball is last touched by Gordon (DEN) prior to it going out of bounds.
Gordon (DEN) brings his arm toward Wembanyama's (SAS) front at the start of the drive before releasing as Wembanayama is able to move through the contact.
Gordon (DEN) legally contests Wembanyama's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Mamukelashvili (SAS) reaches in and brushes Jokic's (DEN) arm, which does not affect his control of the ball as he starts the dribble.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Wembanyama (SAS).
Branham (SAS) commits a take foul on Gordon (DEN).
Wembanyama (SAS) commits a take foul on Jokic (DEN).  The illegal contact occurs during Jokic's shooting motion and should have been assessed as a shooting foul.
Mamukelashvili (SAS) makes incidental contact to Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) arm after deflecting the loose ball during the rebound.
